<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">From India and southern China through southeast Asia, the Philippines and Indonesia to New Guinea and the Solomon Islands in the East, northwards to Japan. Recorded in the study region from China (Fujian, Guangxi*, Guizhou, Hubei, Hunan, Shaanxi, Shanxi, Sichuan, Xizang, Yunnan), India (Nicobar Is), Laos, Taiwan, Thailand, Vietnam.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
